openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Sample API spec
  description: This is a sample API documentation.
  version: 0.0.1
  contact:
    name: Jonh Snow
    url: "/"
    email: john@snow.example.org
paths:
  "/api/v4/admin/loyalty/brands/{brand}/vip/rewards/analytics":
    parameters:
      - name: brand
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
          minimum: 1
        description: The brand ID
    get:
      security:
        - bearerAuth: []
      tags:
        - rewards management
      parameters:
        - name: start
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: date
          example: '2018-07-01'
        - name: end
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: date
          example: '2018-07-02'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Get all analytical numbers
          headers:
            X-Response-Id:
              schema:
                type: string
                format: uuid
              required: true
              description: A unique Id of the response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
        '403':
          description: No access
          headers:
            X-Response-Id:
              schema:
                type: string
                format: uuid
              required: true
              description: A unique Id of the response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
        '500':
          description: Server failed to serve this request due to unresolvable runtime
            condition.
          headers:
            X-Response-Id:
              "$ref": "#/paths/~1api~1v4~1admin~1loyalty~1brands~1%7Bbrand%7D~1vip~1rewards~1analytics/get/responses/403/headers/X-Response-Id"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                "$ref": "#/paths/~1api~1v4~1admin~1loyalty~1brands~1%7Bbrand%7D~1vip~1rewards~1analytics/get/responses/403/content/application~1json/schema"
components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: string
